  m_Name: Speech_MrNorrmalm_Ending
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::ClientSpeech
  Clip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 59e104dde9a3a504b817902714e6087c, type: 3}
  Subtitles: "So anyway, I\u2019ve been wondering about the whole \u2018settling
    down\u2019 thing - Chicks seem to dig it, but I\u2019m not really convinced.
    I miss my girlfriend a lot, and I mean\u2026 I would be fine with her having
    three guys on the side, as long as she came back to me at the end of the day.
    It\u2019s been eating at me - I don\u2019t feel like this one-cucumber-policy
    is working out. Should I try to get back together with her?"
